## 📦 Build & Deployment

### Bootloader Build
```bash
# Configure CMake
cmake -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug

# Build
cmake --build build

# Flash
# Use ST-Link Utility or OpenOCD
```

### MinTool Build
```bash
cd Tool
python build_mintool.bat

# Output: dist/MinTool.exe
```

### SecurityUnlock Build
```bash
cd Tool/SecurityUnlock
python build.bat

# Output: dist/SecurityUnlock.exe
```

